nodes.text: Tara Rueping is a design and concept artist that worked on seasons three and four of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars television series, as well as the video games Star Wars: Bounty Hunter and Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Jedi Academy. She also provided the colors for the cover of the young-readers novel The Clone Wars: Secret Missions 4: Guardians of the Chiss Key.
The ruping animal and the cantina Trueping's from Star Wars: The Clone Wars are named after her.
